{"data":[{"date":"15:22 07/08","title":"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n e ng\u1ea1i con s\u1ed1 4 b\u1edfi theo quan ni\u1ec7m ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 t\u1eed. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y Park, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u khi s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 ai v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4 trong 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 &lsquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rsquo; trong m\u1eaft \u00f4ng Park. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0, nh\u1eefng &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Uzbekistan \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: L\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi gi\u00fap  U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Vinaphone Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i t\u00ecm s\u1ed1 4<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, h\u1ea1, thu, \u0111\u00f4ng th\u00ec trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn sau c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u1ebdo, t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 4 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i chung l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eebng n\u00f3i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' \u1edf ASIAD 2018, v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/vq-01-1640.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 nhanh nh\u1eb9n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi c\u00e1c trung phong tr\u1ebb trung kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai HLV U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;c\u00f2i&rsquo; l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Oman. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n su\u00fdt n\u1eefa \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 82.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Do Hung Dung\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 th\u00ec D\u0169ng &lsquo;ch\u00edp&rsquo; kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c '\u0111\u00e0n em' U23, trong khi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c hay V\u0103n L\u00e2m, n\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tay 3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng, b\u1ea1i. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ed1 4 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Palestine<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 7/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2103","checkdouble":"193944"},{"date":"15:59 07/08","title":"Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/ferdinand-len-tieng-canh-bao-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Rio Ferdinand v\u1eeba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u CEO Ed Woodward d\u1eb9p tan nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Pogba v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Alderweireld v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</h2><h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man United m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 Fred t\u1eeb Shakhtar v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto. Ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Man United. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean Ed Woodward khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea9n \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn thua Bayern Munich h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/ferdinand-len-tieng-canh-bao-man-united.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ed Woodward</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man United \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi. T\u1edd Goal cho bi\u1ebft Alderweireld \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia nh\u1eadp MU nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Mourinho m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford ngay \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Man United c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang \u1edf trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pogba kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a Andre Silva v\u00e0 Yerry Mina t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford k\u00e8m theo 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng Man United kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Ferdinand l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 Ed Woodward</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111ang bao quanh Man United hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ferdinand \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean cho CEO Ed Woodward tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Ferdinand l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u00d4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra h\u1ea3 Ed? Man United l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Pogba. D\u1eadp t\u1eaft ngay nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Alderweireld v\u1ec1 nhanh l\u00ean\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/phil-jones-ha-quyet-tam-gianh-suat-da-chinh-o-mu-172-193930.html\">Phil Jones h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0708-them-mot-cau-thu-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-mu-184-193907.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 07/08: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chia tay MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2102","checkdouble":"193947"},{"date":"15:42 07/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. B\u1edfi v\u1edbi c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</h2><p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Khi b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n 30m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Quang H\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. B\u00f3ng \u0111i xo\u00e1y v\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1eef A \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Uzbekistan d\u00f9 c\u00f3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/photo1517043181499-1517043181499799305547.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Quang H\u1ea3i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa\u00a0</em><i>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u00e9o d\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 120 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vinh quang, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang mong Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp l\u1ea1i si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Trung \u00c1 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3, v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Uzbekistan, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f2i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169, cho d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. D\u1eabu sao m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chinh ph\u1ee5c ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Do \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u00e1i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u2018c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Tuy\u1ebft\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\">S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f2n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m mang phong c\u00e1ch trivela c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Vinaphone Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/U23-Viet-Nam-Cho-mot-duong-cong-cua-nguoi-dac-biet-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat c\u1ee7a V-League 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. 6 th\u00e1ng sau ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u00fd song Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 20 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha tung ch\u00e2n ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Cup Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1edfi lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Quang H\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2101","checkdouble":"193948"},{"date":"16:07 07/08","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mang th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Sau khi nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia h\u1ea1n b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1edd th\u00eam 12 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n Courtois v\u1ec1 d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n bao g\u1ed3m Keylor Navas, Kiko Casilla c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 2 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb l\u00e0 Andriy Lunin v\u00e0 Luca Zidane. N\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Courtois, Los Blancos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chelsea-muon-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-cua-Athletic-Bilbao-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Courtois th\u00ec \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t. Th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, anh y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Real. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1ecf r\u00f5 l\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea th\u00ec d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t ch\u1ec9 nh\u1ea3 Courtois n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi l\u00fac th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi (9/8). Sau Jordan Pickford c\u1ee7a Everton hay Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Bilbao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Oblak, The Blues s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u201cx\u00e9\u201d h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra l\u00ean t\u1edbi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (80 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, su\u00fdt n\u1eefa Kepa \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua song b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Zinedine Zidane. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Kepa \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bilbao v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Basque.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khung-khiep-chelsea-chi-89-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-courtois-172-193897.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp: Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: \u201cCourtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2100","checkdouble":"193949"},{"date":"16:39 07/08","title":"V\u00ec \u201cmi\u1ebfng b\u00e1nh\u201d b\u00e9o b\u1edf n\u00e0y, Modric t\u00ednh b\u1ecf Real sang Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan. Nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia d\u00e0nh cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ea7n 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter d\u00f9ng \u201cm\u1ed3i ngon\u201d chi\u00eau d\u1ee5</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd AS c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi t\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u0103ng g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 trong m\u01a1 sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Inter \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (10 tri\u1ec7u Euro)/ n\u0103m cho Modric. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 1985 ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5,8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (6,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro) m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/luka-modric-tinh-roi-real-sang-inter-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Inter d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn thu h\u00fat Modric</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1edbi Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c 2 n\u0103m. Anh s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1c. Vi\u1ec7c Inter \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi 4 n\u0103m, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Modric bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam n\u1eefa, Inter c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u Modric sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. C\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Nerazzurri hi\u1ec7n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Modric b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuka Modric d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real Madrid khi CLB tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. D\u00f9 sao, n\u1ebfu Real kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1eafp 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Luka-Modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Luka Modric t\u00ednh r\u1eddi Real sang Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Real t\u1eeb Tottenham v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, Modric \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 Champions League, 1 La Liga c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00ean t\u1edbi 670 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (750 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, Modric tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n ra nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Real. Song khi m\u00e0 Inter Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u sau 6 n\u0103m, Modric v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 7 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Inter Milan tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\">Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-hoi-mua-hau-ve-mu-172-193679.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/chinh-thuc-nguoi-hung-world-cup-se-doi-dau-ronaldo-o-y-184-192442.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ronaldo \u1edf \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-spalletti-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-inter-176-192251.html\">HLV Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2099","checkdouble":"193950"},{"date":"16:36 07/08","title":"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-cho-mot-duong-cong-cua-nguoi-dac-biet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. B\u1edfi v\u1edbi c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u00e0 t\u1ed1i nay nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</h2><p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Khi b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n 30m so v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Quang H\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. B\u00f3ng \u0111i xo\u00e1y v\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1eef A \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Uzbekistan d\u00f9 c\u00f3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/photo1517043181499-1517043181499799305547.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Quang H\u1ea3i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa\u00a0</em><i>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u00e9o d\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 120 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vinh quang, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u00f2ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn \u0111ang mong Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp l\u1ea1i si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Trung \u00c1 nhi\u1ec1u duy\u00ean n\u1ee3, v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Uzbekistan, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f2i m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169, cho d\u00f9 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. D\u1eabu sao m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chinh ph\u1ee5c ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y, b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mang theo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Do \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Quang H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u00e1i l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u2018c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng Tuy\u1ebft\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park-168-193944.html\">S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTheo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, c\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f2n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m mang phong c\u00e1ch trivela c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Vinaphone Cup.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/U23-Viet-Nam-Cho-mot-duong-cong-cua-nguoi-dac-biet-hinh-anh-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat c\u1ee7a V-League 2018, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. 6 th\u00e1ng sau ng\u00e0y th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League 2018, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u00fd song Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 20 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League 2018 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha tung ch\u00e2n ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Cup Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1edfi lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Quang H\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2098","checkdouble":"193951"},{"date":"17:08 07/08","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: C\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/joe-hart-roi-man-city-den-burnley.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Burnley. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 31 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi The Clarets v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hart b\u1ecb Man City h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Joe Hart t\u1ea1i Man City tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u0103m t\u1ed1i. Anh b\u1ecb g\u1ea1t ra kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u00ecm CLB m\u1edbi. V\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Guardiola, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2n t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 Hart th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Hart ch\u01a1i cho Torino t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua \u0111\u1ee9t. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City, Hart \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Burnley h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Burnley h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/Joe-Hart-roi-Man-City-den-Burnley-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joe Hart kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City xem tr\u1ecdng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Guardiola v\u1ec1 anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Hart kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Man City trong tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi Chelsea. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Burnley</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3, c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi Joe Hart n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Man City. Ngay sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Burnley \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, c\u00e1c b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joe Hart den Burnley\" title=\"Joe Hart den Burnley\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/joe-hart-roi-man-city-den-burnley.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Burnley</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u00f4ng tin Joe Hart r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Burnley \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng 75 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Sean Dyche d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hart kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 song theo gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, n\u00f3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBurnley xem Hart nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Nick Pope, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb tr\u1eadt kh\u1edbp vai \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Aberdeen t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Europa League v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng. M\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor l\u00e0 Tom Heaton v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHart l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Burnley trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Ben Gibson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-172-193954.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga-172-193949.html\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha-172-193931.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u0129 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Wilfried Zaha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/nong-paul-pogba-dat-thoa-thuan-voi-barca-187-193906.html\">N\u00f3ng: Paul Pogba \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-laurent-koscielny-172-193898.html\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Laurent Koscielny?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2097","checkdouble":"193952"},{"date":"17:40 07/08","title":"Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/harry-kane-that-vong-voi-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Harry Kane th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mauricio Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kane gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 25 tu\u1ed5i g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd thua Croatia 2-1 trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990 t\u1edbi nay, Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i \u0111i t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho Kane, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mang b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam s\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/harry-kane-that-vong-voi-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Kane kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 b\u1edfi 3 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a anh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u00e0 1 t\u1eeb penalty tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kane kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Harry Kane th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y Mauricio Pochettino c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cKane r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate Harry Kane\" title=\"Gareth Southgate Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/123.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Harry Kane th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 3, d\u00e0nh h\u1eb3n 5 gi\u1edd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Jesus Perez (tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pochettino). T\u00f4i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Kane v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i: Kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i n\u00f3i: Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Kane \u0111\u00e1p: V\u00e2ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi Kane. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t qu\u00fd tr\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng CLB sau World Cup. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i Kane song c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Harry Kane tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-nham-2-sao-khung-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-nang-cap-hang-cong-172-192466.html\">Real nh\u1eafm 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cdv-real-madrid-muon-harry-kane-thay-the-cristiano-ronaldo-180-192176.html\">C\u0110V Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n Harry Kane thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-noi-gi-khi-tottenham-quyet-dinh-dung-ngoai-ttcn-172-191864.html\">Harry Kane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Tottenham quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i TTCN?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giay-vang-world-cup-an-dinh-ngay-tai-xuat-san-co-172-191816.html\">Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng World Cup \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2096","checkdouble":"193953"},{"date":"16:51 07/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-nhuong-mu-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra t\u1ea1i Man United tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 N\u0103m t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Harry Maguire \u0111\u1ebfn Man United\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-nhung-ngay-cuoi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Maguire kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng d\u1ea7n l\u00ean sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Maguire l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Southgate s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Maguire \u0111ang m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t d\u1ea7n khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Maguire c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecb Tottenham t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gi\u1edd ch\u00f3t cho Leicester \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Maguire.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Marcos Rojo \u0111\u1ebfn Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd Marcos Rojo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Man United. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi ng\u1edd Rojo \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEverton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng PSG \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-mu-tag2331.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU</span> g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y cho th\u1ea5y Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho vi\u1ec7c thanh l\u00fd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEverton \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rojo th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Smalling ho\u1eb7c Lindelof c\u1ee7a Man United. Nh\u1eefng&nbsp; tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Martial \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea ho\u1eb7c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Martial\" title=\"tien dao Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-58-bang-chung-cho-thay-martial-sap-roi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Martial \u0111ang r\u1ea5t m\u01a1 h\u1ed3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1i gai trong m\u1eaft HLV Jose Mourinho l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu con trai ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, Martial kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Bayern h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa Martial v\u00e0 Mourinho d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o h\u00e0n g\u1eafn n\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng Man United \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 Willian b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch g\u00e1n Martial v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Martial kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford hay kh\u00f4ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Alderweireld \u0111\u1ebfn Man United\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toby Alderweireld\" title=\"Toby Alderweireld\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/5-thuong-vu-co-the-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ttcn-tai-anh-dong-cua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1ea3y ra r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alderweireld c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gia nh\u1eadp Man United cao nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Daniel Levy c\u1ee7a Spurs n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f2i 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea3 Alderweireld. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ki\u00ean tr\u00ec thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Spurs.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf cho Alderweireld. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, Alderweireld c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i gia nh\u1eadp Man United.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian \u0111\u1ebfn Man United</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 Man United c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u01b0ng \u00fd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y nh\u1ee9c nh\u1ed1i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng Willian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. United \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Willian kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Man City t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, Willian \u0111\u00e3 \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean t\u1edd Goal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u1ea1i b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbng Mourinho m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu Chelsea th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU&nbsp;kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ferdinand-len-tieng-canh-bao-man-united-172-193947.html\">Ferdinand \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chot-120-trieu-euro-cho-nguoi-thay-the-pogba-172-193895.html\">MU ch\u1ed1t 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Pogba</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2095","checkdouble":"193954"},{"date":"17:46 07/08","title":"Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/real-madrid-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-hai-nguoi-hung-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao Croatia Luka Modric v\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Bernabeu b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n ra \u0111i trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0a Croatia l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real Madrid r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng Luka Modric v\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong n\u0103m nay, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Cristiano Ronaldo.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Real Madrid n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Real Madrid n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/real-madrid-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-hai-nguoi-hung-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Real Madrid n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean khi ch\u01b0a x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5m ra sao t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i ngay trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Trong khi Modric \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter Milan s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n g\u1eaft gao th\u00ec nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n b\u1ecf t\u1eadp nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh r\u1ed1i ren \u1edf Bernabeu th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho Modric v\u00e0 Kovacic. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Los Blancos \u2013 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 g\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Atletico Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Modric v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u1edbi m\u1ebb hay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c h\u1ebft, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i ri\u00eang t\u01b0 v\u1edbi Modric v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Kovacic, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f9a vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho CLB. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i n\u00e0o h\u1ebft nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed th\u00eau d\u1ec7t, Modric v\u00e0 Kovacic s\u1ebd h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real Madrid.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mua-he-am-dam-cua-real-madrid-sau-dinh-cao-la-vuc-sau-180-192564.html\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Real Madrid: Sau \u0111\u1ec9nh cao l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n nh\u01b0 v\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2094","checkdouble":"193955"},{"date":"10:08 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-astana-vs-dinamo-zagreb-21h00-ngay-78-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb 21h00 ng\u00e0y 78 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb 21h00 ng\u00e0y 78 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Astana-vs-Dinamo-Zagreb.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Astana vs Dinamo Zagreb: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>X\u00e9t t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, Astana kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec v\u1edbi Dinamo Zagreb. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Dinamo Zagreb \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Croatia, n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 \u0110TQG g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, th\u00ec Astana  ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kazakhstan, qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o di\u1ec7n th\u1ea5p k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba gi\u00e0 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 117 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ea4y v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1eafm vai c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Astana c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ed3i chi\u1ebfu tr\u00ean. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hryhorchuk s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m h\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu, Astana c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u CLB trung b\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch quen t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ghi danh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League (2015/16). B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2018/19, Astana \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Sutjeska Niksic c\u1ee7a Montenegro v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110an M\u1ea1ch - Midtjyland \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hryhorchuk to\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 TLCA, Astana r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng tin v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Xa h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 10, thua 2 \u1edf 12 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Dinamo Zagreb th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1/6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua), n\u00ean Astana t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng cho m\u00ecnh \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2093","checkdouble":"193922"},{"date":"10:31 07/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t, Pochettino v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Tottenham v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 Champions League h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.</h2><h2>Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Spurs \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 ho\u1eb7c th\u1ee9 3 trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang quen d\u1ea7n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Spurs c\u0169ng \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 s\u00e1t Leicester trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf m\u00f9a 2015/16 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho th\u1ea5y Spurs c\u00f3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Villa Park m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f2n \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/mauricio-pochettino-27.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Pochettino</span> v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1c quan. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cN\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng HLV c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Vi\u1ec7c mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 hai vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Champions League 3 n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee9. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 4 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0m t\u00f4i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u sau 4 n\u0103m n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-172-193891.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: MU \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-sap-co-tan-binh-voi-gia-18-trieu-bang-172-193870.html\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-180-193833.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2092","checkdouble":"193924"},{"date":"10:16 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Standard Liege vs Ajax 01h00 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-standard-liege-vs-ajax-01h00-ngay-88-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (7/8). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Eden Hazard</h2>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n b\u1ea5n lo\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh vung ti\u1ec1n mua Eden Hazard trong th\u1eddi gian \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c m\u1ecdi n\u0103m, c\u1eeda chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Premier League 2018/19 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng v\u00e0o 17h th\u1ee9 N\u0103m n\u00e0y (9/8) gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi tranh, thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn 31/8 nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi n\u0103m.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 78, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 78, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Chelsea-muon-mua-Isco-va-Asensio-thay-the-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Eden Hazard</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n 2 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa - 1 trung v\u1ec7, 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi n\u00e0o. Theo t\u1edd Don Balon, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eadt Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, MU mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ecdn Jan Oblak thay Courtois</h2>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng khai mong mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. The Blues v\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Jan Oblak c\u1ee7a Atletico l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn. Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovenia kh\u1ecfi Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Oblak v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, Courtois s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p gia nh\u1eadp Real ngay H\u00e8 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 \u00fd nguy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i d\u00f9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu n\u00e0o v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a v\u00ec anh s\u1ebd h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khung-khiep-chelsea-chi-89-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-courtois-172-193897.html\">Kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp: Chelsea chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Barca kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n sao 140 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ousmane Dembele th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. Ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb RAC1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u1edf h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eebng mua v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 140 tri\u1ec7u euro \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n<h2>Inter Milan chi \u0111\u1eadm v\u00ec Modric</h2>\r\nT\u1edd La Sexta cho hay, Inter Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 Modric m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 10 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Modric t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi ph\u00ed 15 tri\u1ec7u euro k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o h\u00e8 2019.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 78 MU b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 78 MU b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-78-MU-bat-ngo-theo-duoi-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chia tay th\u00eam 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Calum Chambers chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Fulham theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 n\u0103m. Chambers l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo chia tay Arsenal sau Chuba Akpom, Santi Cazorla, Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Per Mertesacker.\r\n<h2>Witsel c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Dortmund</h2>\r\nCh\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c cho Tianjin Quanjian, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Axel Witsel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.\r\n<h2>Sao Milan t\u1edbi Atletico ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf</h2>\r\nTheo chuy\u00ean gia chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Di Marzio, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nikola Kalinic s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Madrid l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Atletico trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Atletico s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kalinic 1 m\u00f9a k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro. Sau khi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, Rojiblancos nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Kevin Gameiro t\u1edbi Valencia.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2091","checkdouble":"193925"},{"date":"10:40 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava 01h30 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-crvena-zvezda-vs-trnava-01h30-ngay-88-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava 01h30 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava 01h30 ng\u00e0y 88 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Crvena-Zvezda-vs-Trnava.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Crvena Zvezda vs Trnava: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Crvena Zvezda n\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Serbia ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Sao \u0111\u1ecf Beograde n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u0103m n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169 khi t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1 (1990/91). V\u00ec th\u1ebf, v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, vi\u1ec7c Crvena Zvezda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean l\u00e0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB c\u1ee7a Serbia to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, v\u00e0 5 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t (kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch tr\u00ean 1 b\u00e0n). H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Crvena Zvezda lu\u00f4n khoan th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn \u1edf c\u1ea3 6 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Trnava, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i Legia Warszawa c\u1ee7a Ba Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2 n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Slovakia gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c Crvena Zvezda ph\u1ea3i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Khi \u1ea5y, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Trnava s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng b\u1edfi Crvena Zvezda s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 Legia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCrvena Zvezda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 sau \u0111\u00e2y 1 tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2090","checkdouble":"193927"},{"date":"10:52 07/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nottingham vs West Brom 01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-nottingham-vs-west-brom-01h45-ngay-88-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Nottingham vs West Brom l\u00fac 01h45 ng\u00e0y 8/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nottingham vs West Brom 01h45 ng\u00e0y 88 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nottingham vs West Brom 01h45 ng\u00e0y 88 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Nottingham-vs-West-Brom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nottingham vs West Brom</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Nottingham vs West Brom: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Championship 2018/19, West Brom \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Bolton nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2 ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 The Hawthorns. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Darren Moore. C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 n\u00e0y khi ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Nottingham Forest. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, Nottingham th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u1edf Championship m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n t\u1edbi 8 t\u00e2n binh. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB mang t\u00ean Joao Carvalho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Benfica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, Nottingham s\u1edf d\u0129 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u \u00e1i v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n West Brom \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 (h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Bristol). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Aitor Karanka \u0111\u00e3 4 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Nottingham thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a lu\u00f4n t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Nottingham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 10/23 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Brom ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1edfi trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng, The Baggies kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua Bolton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Darren Moore s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ea1ch 5 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 (th\u1eafng 4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng song West Brom v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Kieran Gibbs, Robson-Kanu, Morrison, Bartley, Livermore, Rondon hay Hegazi. V\u1edbi d\u00e0n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Nottingham, West Brom \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Nottingham v\u00e0 West Brom \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. 6/8 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Nottingham th\u1eafng 3/4 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 West Brom g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (th\u1eafng 3, thua 1).<br>\r\n- 4/6 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n- West Brom th\u1eafng 3/4 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nottingham (th\u1eafng 3, thua 1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\n- Nottingham Forest: V\u1eafng Hillel Soudani.<br>\r\n- West Brom: V\u1eafng Nacer Chadli v\u00e0 Salomon Rondon.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2089","checkdouble":"193928"}]}